  "abstract": "On November 21, 2018, the Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System (Board) published a final rule in the Federal Register regarding the Large Financial Institution Rating System. That document included two typographical errors in \"Appendix A--Text of Large Financial Institution Rating System\" relating to the description of the conditionally meets expectation rating. This document corrects those typographical errors.",
